    <p>{`Obtain the baseline model for hand and pocket data using `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`Leave One Subject Out(LOSO)`}</inlineCode>{` and `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`hold out`}</inlineCode>{` validation separately. The classifier we decide to use is `}<strong parentName="p">{`RandomForest`}</strong>{`.`}</p>
