      <li parentName="ul">{`We train a model with hand data only and evaluate using LOSO. `}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`In order to justify the poor performance of LOSO, we also evaluate using hold out validation(subject dependent). i.e. we train only on Subject 1 and test on Subject 1 data using a 70:30 split of the dataset. Similarly for all the other subjects as well.`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`We perform the same set of experiments using pocket data.`}</li>
