    }}>{`Baseline`}</h3>
    <p>{`We obtain baseline model for training on hand data of each subject separately and testing on pocket data of that corresponding subject with a RandomForest classifer. This becomes the baseline for Experiment 2 where we try to build a robust classifier to account for sensor placement variations for individual subjects. We can see that the performance of the classifier is very low as shown in the plot, which is expected because when we train a model to recognize activity by recording data with mobile phone on hand from a single subject and then test it on data recorded with mobile phone in pocket, the accuracy is bound to be low.`}</p>
